      </p>
      <div class="card-actions">
        <a class="btn" href="https://www.instagram.com/mentalharmonyorg?igsh=bzM5bGlnYzJyZXM1" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Open Instagram
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <!-- MYPacademy -->
    <article class="card card-stretch">
      <div class="kicker">Organization</div>
      <h3 style="margin:6px 0 8px">MYPacademy</h3>
      <p class="p">
        Resources for the MYP curriculum. Instagram: <b>@mypacademy.official</b>.
        For email queries: <a href="mailto:themypacademy@gmail.com">themypacademy@gmail.com</a>.
